Defendant Andrew Nmi Pena in court with attorney Jamy Richard Johansen.  Bruce Robert Poquette appeared for the State of Wisconsin.    State moved to amend to 948.40(1) contributing to the delinquiency of a child.  Court grants motion to amend.  defendant entered plea of no contest.  DE advised of rights and penalties; DE waives rights; parties stipulate to facts   Court finds defendant guilty.

Arraignment scheduled for February 23, 2016 at 10:00 am.
